title: Is JFK Jr Back Yet? Sesame Street = BIG PHARMA? 11.9.21

description:
In episode 1026, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Jenny Zigrino to discuss AstroWorld, what happened?, Speaking of Texas- Shit keeps getting weirder in Dallas with the QAnon folks…, Jenna “I’m TOO White For Prison” Ellis is READY for prison y’all!, Do people like AMC Theater popcorn THIS much? Anti-Vaxxers Have Been Attacking Sesame Street For a While Now and more!

  1. Astroworld: Travis Scott and Drake sued over deadly Texas concert crush
  2. Within minutes, the Astroworld Festival turned deadly. Here's what we know about the show's timeline
  3. Travis Scott will refund all Astroworld tickets, cancels Vegas show
  4. Speaking of Texas- Shit keeps getting weirder in Dallas with the QAnon folks…
  5. Jenna “I’m TOO White For Prison” Ellis is READY for prison y’all!
  6. Do people like AMC Theater popcorn THIS much?
  7. Anti-Vaxxers Have Been Attacking Sesame Street For a While Now 
  8. Ted Cruz condemns Big Bird for advocating Covid vaccines for kids
  9. Newsmax to Implement COVID-19 Vaccine Mandate After Weeks of Attacking Vaccine Mandates
  10. Sesame Workshop, the Ad Council, COVID Collaborative and CDC Launch New PSAs About COVID-19 Vaccines
